{"word":"σκηνόω","slug":"σκηνόω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>σκηνόω</b></el> <el>(σκηνόω,) ( φυτ. <el>-ώσω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:σκηνή'><el>σκηνή</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to pitch tents, encamp</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>= <a href='S:σκηνέω'><el>σκηνέω</el></a>, <i>to dwell in a tent</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>: generally, <i>to settle, take up one's abode</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>:—in <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> <i>to live</i> or <i>be</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to occupy with tents</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}